{"tid":2193850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普砲轟美軍高層 ︰只想發動戰爭讓軍火商開心","createTime":"2020-09-08T06:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T12:36:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":138,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"46553cf547cc23de36b4cb3dcc6abbd0694a7796","tid":2193850,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:58:14.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普與五角大廈關係緊張之際，他又對美軍批評，指美軍高層只想繼續發動戰爭，以便能讓軍火商開心。<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n他表示，「我並不是說軍人們都愛我。士兵們愛我，但五角大樓高層可能不愛我，因為他們只想打仗，什麼也不想做，所以全部製造炸彈、飛機以及其他一切的出色公司，都能保持開心。」<br />\n<br />\nCNN 報導，這是川普對自己任命的軍方領導層發起前所未有的攻擊，川普與五角大廈領導層之間的關係變得愈來愈緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3285143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3285143&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=71f282fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3285143&h=6a1d98ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3285143</a>"},{"pid":"dc5645db7daba8f0ebb2b52683a2616d2501a5d6","tid":2193850,"uid":21545,"like":151,"dislike":3,"score":148,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"CNN<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88521cb4e0fcfd30ff05bb54ab1ee77ec2a6293","tid":2193850,"uid":294518,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"挑撥軍方與侵關係"},{"pid":"920846311516bfa8d1cc2b011c9e601f1c7a8b32","tid":2193850,"uid":270889,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"侵拎和平獎啦"},{"pid":"21239e0c7f463f61ed488a002d2e148ee8a46969","tid":2193850,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6f3115fa0d9ce3a9ca4914b6990f472d9f2a81","tid":2193850,"uid":251732,"like":6,"dislike":4,"scor